STATE
v.
WILLINGHAM 2019-0900 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

APPEAL ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appellant's motion to consolidate with case No. 2019-0659 granted. French, J., would accept the cause on proposition of law No. I only.

Donnelly, J., dissents and would not accept the appeal.
